A '''Daddy''' in [[LGBT culture|gay culture]] is a [[LGBT slang|slang]] term meaning an (typically) older man sexually involved in a relationship or wanting sex with a younger male. The age gap may differ, but the relationship involves the traditional parental hierarchy of father-son dynamics, the daddy providing emotional support and guidance along with sexual encouragement and nurturing to the inexperienced and vulnerable partner.

Often these relationships are categorized as either "DADDY and [[Boi (slang)|boi]]" or "DAD and son," although this is not absolute, and some relationships prefer no labels.  Dad, or Daddy, are completely different from the similarly labeled [[wikt:sugar daddy|sugar daddy]], although this can sometimes lead to some confusion.

